  "text": "MTORC1 inhibition not only upregulates autophagy, but also macropinocytosis, a process by which nutrient-limited, Ras-driven cancer cells endocytose, envelop extracellular protein, and release AAs through lysosome-mediated degradation, paradoxically fueling growth of cancer cells [CITATION_1] . We next asked whether or not DQ661 would increase lysosomal catabolism of extracellular proteins since it inhibits mTORC1.",
